detaileddescription.para: Set the title of this axis.

Define the Font to be used for the title. Can be used as a group property: titleFont{bold:true,family:"Arial",pointSize:16} See QML's documentation for details on its basic Font type: http://qt-project.org/doc/qt-5/qml-font.html
The color of the title text.
If aspectRatio is larger than 0, the axis will enforce this ratio at all times. Note: aspectRatio = x/y

If true, the automatic axis limits will fit the plots in the axis as tightly as possible. If false, the axis will round the y-axis up to whole numbers (dependent on the scale of the axis). E.g. 894 -> 900, 8894 -> 9000
